response.original_title: Lick Library: Guitar Techniques - Van Halen
response.overview: Learn 50 trademark Van Halen guitar licks with Stuart Bull. This excellent two hour guitar lesson course will teach you some of the guitar techniques that influenced a million rock guitarists!  Lessons include: two handed tapping, tremolo picking, screaming harmonics and much more. If you're looking to take your playing to the next level, this guitar lesson course will provide you with an arsenal of Van Halen style licks that you can incorporate into your rock soloing repertoire!!
